    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont really have time for blood tests right now and honestly its kind of annoying to deal with doctors just for some vitamins. if i felt fine and i just want to prep for flu season, would 50k iu for like 2 weeks really be that dangerous? i've read online that some people do massive doses to 'reset' their system.",
